  "description": "MCP server for SearchAtlas AI Agent — SEO, content, PPC, and site management tools. Exposes 16 tools for keyword research, site auditing, content optimization, backlink analysis, OTTO SEO automation, rank tracking, Google Business Profile management, and LLM brand visibility monitoring.",
